{#                        Your browser does not support the audio element.#}
{#                    </audio>#}
                    <p style="margin-top:35px;">Copyright &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} All Rights Reserved by Wandering
                        Loyalty and Moon Whale Media Recordings</p>

                </div>

                <div class="nobottommargin">
                    <div class="feature-box media-box">
                        <div class="fbox-media" style="margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
                            <p style="font-family:Quicksand; font-size: 18px; color:#333;">
                                All of your lies,<br/>
                                You lived them all.<br/>
                                All of my sighs,<br/>
                                You chose to stall.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-family:Quicksand; font-size: 18px; color:#333;">
                                Secrecy and betrayal,<br/>
                                When they set sail, lift up the veil.<br/>
                                Secrecy and betrayal,<br/>
                                When they’re dead, they tell no tales.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-family:Quicksand; font-size: 18px; color:#333;">
                                Showed no respect,<br/>
                                For my blue heart,<br/>
                                Used with deflect,<br/>
                                You played your part.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-family:Quicksand; font-size: 18px; color:#333;">
                                Secrecy and betrayal,<br/>
                                When they set sail, lift up the veil.<br/>
                                Secrecy and betrayal,<br/>
                                When they’re dead, they tell no tales.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-family:Quicksand; font-size: 18px; color:#333;">
                                Longing for trust,<br/>
                                I thought I knew,<br/>
                                Your secrets scarred,<br/>
                                Me like so few.
                            </p>
                            <p style="font-family:Quicksand; font-size: 18px; color:#333;">
                                Secrecy and betrayal,<br/>
                                When they set sail, lift up the veil.<br/>
                                Secrecy and betrayal,<br/>
                                When they’re dead, they tell no tales.
                            </p>
                            <p style="color:#333; margin-top:35px;">Copyright &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} All Rights
                                Reserved by Wandering
                                Loyalty and Moon Whale Media Recordings</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

